{"tid":2361712,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院擬表決要求彭斯宣布特朗普無法履職","createTime":"2021-01-11T02:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T05:52:17.000Z","uid":70964,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6d4c4a38591fec2793ce8e0da2d791c30c985b7b","tid":2361712,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"美國國會山莊發生5人死亡的暴力衝擊事件後，眾議院議長波洛西計劃就一項決議案進行表決，促請副總統彭斯及內閣，啟動憲法第25條修正案，宣布總統特朗普無法履行職務，將他免職。預料眾議院的民主黨人會尋求簡單多數表決通過，但很大機會遭到共和黨阻止，要求記名表決。波洛西預計，民主黨佔多數的眾議院，會通過要求免去特朗普職務的決議，如果通過後，即使彭斯沒有行動，他亦需要在24小時內回應。波洛西揚言，若果彭斯不採取行動，她會推動眾議院展開彈劾總統程序。據報已有210名眾議員支持彈劾，接近眾議院的多數。另外，先後有兩名共和黨參議員倒戈，要求特朗普辭職。"},{"pid":"ad1a07b0980c465c89256a2fd2ac3ad15bb42132","tid":2361712,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T02:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0400cb6bff62dbdf582e820f87d79f266c841878","tid":2361712,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T02:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b795c892dc350037c489109e77d31b103b16f424","tid":2361712,"uid":10637,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T02:45:53.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/